    <briefdescription>
<para>Type-erasing wrapper that adapts a plain system type to the <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1System" kindref="compound">System</ref> interface. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1TypedSystem" kindref="compound">TypedSystem</ref> owns an instance of T by value and delegates the abstract `initSystem()` / `updateSystem()` calls from <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1System" kindref="compound">System</ref> to `T::init()` and `T::update()` respectively.</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>`T::update(UpdateContext&amp;)` is **required** (enforced via `static_assert`).</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>`T::init(GameWorld&amp;)` is **optional** (detected via the <ref refid="concepthelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1HasInit" kindref="compound">HasInit</ref> concept).</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>The <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1SystemRegistry" kindref="compound">SystemRegistry</ref> creates `TypedSystem&lt;T&gt;` internally; user code never interacts with this wrapper directly.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>T</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The concrete system type. Must satisfy <ref refid="concepthelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1HasUpdate" kindref="compound">HasUpdate</ref>.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1System" kindref="compound">System</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1SystemRegistry" kindref="compound">SystemRegistry</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="concepthelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1HasInit" kindref="compound">HasInit</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="concepthelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1HasUpdate" kindref="compound">HasUpdate</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
